Details:
This is my remake of Beaver Creek from Halo 2. I have worked on this map over the course of 4 years, on 5 different computers, and i do believe its finally finished. There was a time when i never thought i'd say that hahaha. Enjoy! Specs:
40 spawns, teleporters, spawned weapons, custom textures and skybox, and a whole lot more.
Please visit Clan 5k3's studio for more Halo css maps and materials.
